________________________________________________________________________

Simple static content server (HTML, CSS, JS + images)

See https://github.com/imlinus/personal for an example in action


Install
________________________________________________________________________

mkdir modules
cd modules
git submodule add https://github.com/imlinus/site-generator.git


Usage
________________________________________________________________________

import server from './modules/static-server/source/index.js'

server({
  src: '/build',
  port: 1337,
  main: 'index.html'
})
